title: FaceStore for Android Wear
summary: Full collection of Android Wear faces.
description: Full collection of Android Wear faces.Android Wear is fun! but It is not easy to find beautiful watch faces for my precious wear device.We just want to make this process simple. We will spend time on searching and organizing watch faces and deliver to you you like watch catalog.
descriptionHTML:
Full collection of Android Wear faces.

Android Wear is fun! but It is not easy to find beautiful watch faces for my precious wear device.

We just want to make this process simple. We will spend time on searching and organizing watch faces and deliver to you you like watch catalog.
comments: Great concept for an app that bypasses the need to use similar websites to view watch faces but the app is dead as it cannot load any data and should be removed from the Play Store since it's clearly been abandoned.
Broken The show your watch section will not upload.  Please fix, been broken for months.
Unstable Slow loading and frequent force close
Great app. Was able to find many faces that are not available without searching for hours.  Thanks guys.
Doesn't work Won't show any faces when I select all faces.
Not working Originally had 5 stars, now just force closes. Needs to be fixed
